      • getEventsRequestObject

        public static BoxEventRequestObject getEventsRequestObject(long streamPosition)
        Construct a new events object for fetching the event stream.
        Parameters:
        streamPosition - Stream position. See http://developers.box.com/docs/#events for how to set this. To set this to "now", use BoxEventRequestObject.STREAM_POSITION_NOW.Don't use STREAM_POSITION_NOW if you are requesting for enterprise events(admin_logs),STREAM_POSITION_NOW is only supported for regular events.
        Returns:
        BoxEventRequestObject.
